aurynk (1.0.2) noble; urgency=medium

  * Release v1.0.2 — fixes and improvements
  * Fix UnboundLocalError in actions.mirror_device
  * Ensure main-window → tray synchronization by exposing app-bound send_status_to_tray
  * Make tray command listener stoppable so app.quit exits cleanly
  * Add PID fallback in tray helper so Quit still works if socket IPC fails
  * Flatpak: update manifest to point at v1.0.2 source archive
  * Misc: UI and packaging fixes

